TICTeC needs you!!!! Submit your paper now!!
首次在亞洲舉辦的 TICTeC 九月將在台北登場，別錯過分享你的研究和計畫的機會，邀稿期限倒數九天~ https://goo.gl/6OT02b
story: Lulu Keng shared 開放文化基金會's post to the group: g0v.tw 後勤中心.
description:
[Final Call for Paper Submission, Deadline: June 16]
Only 9 days left to submit a session proposal to TICTeC@Taipei!! Share your stories and findings about civic tech, open data, and open government with us in Taipei.
⏰⏰⏰
倒數九天，快來 TICTeC@Taipei 和我們分享你在公民科技、開放資料、開放政府等等主題的故事！

📣 Submit a talk here >>  https://goo.gl/6OT02b
✈️ Submit a travel grant application >> https://goo.gl/KUw31m
😎 Learn more about TICTeC (公民科技動能推升研討會) >> http://civictechfest.org/
